title: Flying Karamazov Brothers Showtime Special
description:
Taken from a 30 year old VHS tape with a mediocre laptop using a USB capture unit and a 15 year old VCR.  I may make a real DVD with chapters and such someday, but in case I never do, I'm sharing it as is.

These guys inspired me to learn to juggle, I hope they inspire you in some way as well.  

The cast has changed through the years, but check out their site for tour date information.  You won't regret it!
